summary: Completed comprehensive end-to-end testing of SimplyComply UK compliance platform. All backend APIs (17/17) and frontend features tested successfully. Full user flow from signup through onboarding to dashboard working correctly.
passed_tests: Landing page loads with navigation, hero, sectors, features, pricing
User signup flow creates account and redirects to onboarding
User login flow authenticates and redirects appropriately
Onboarding flow allows sector selection and business setup
Dashboard displays business information and compliance progress
Protected routes redirect to login when not authenticated
All 17 backend API endpoints return correct responses
